In cases where TPB is down, at least for uploading, I will often post initially to KAT.

So, if my CWKO torrent doesn't show up here in a reasonable amount of time, you can check http://kat.ph/usearch/Countdown%20with%20Keith%20Olbermann/

You can also check https://forum.suprbay.org/showthread.php?tid=113586 to see if I've left a message there.
The resolution of this crappily-cropped file is actually 512 x 288.
